{"id":46719,"date":"2025-01-30T13:56:04","date_gmt":"2025-01-30T18:56:04","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/jamesclear.com\/?post_type=3-2-1&#038;p=46719"},"modified":"2025-01-30T13:56:05","modified_gmt":"2025-01-30T18:56:05","slug":"january-30-2025","status":"publish","type":"3-2-1","link":"https:\/\/jamesclear.com\/3-2-1\/january-30-2025","title":{"rendered":"3-2-1: On the danger of a good idea, how to do your best work, and a question to inspire action"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<h2 id=\"h-3-ideas-from-me\">3 IDEAS FROM ME<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>I.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>&#8220;Beware the student of one teacher. A good idea spirals into dogma when it gets applied to everything and stretched beyond the areas where it is useful. Remain open and embrace a lot of teachers.&#8221;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>(<\/em>\u200b<a href=\"https:\/\/ctt.ac\/bfdFL\">\u200b<em>Share this on X<\/em>\u200b\u200b<\/a><em>)<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p>\u200bII.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>&#8220;Your best performances will come when you are working in a way that is a full expression of you. The work becomes a natural display of your personality. This is when you not only get better results, but also love the activity \u2014 because in doing the craft, you feel alive.&#8221;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p>III.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>&#8220;People can sometimes be held hostage by their expectations. They have a dream of something they would like to achieve or a path they intend to follow, but their mindset falls apart when things don&#8217;t work out how they had hoped.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The key is to reach for an extremely high bar, but to be adaptable enough to reframe the failures, disappointments, and defeats into fuel for the next thing. Give your best effort, but no matter how it works out, trust that life will be good for you. Focus on how the world is working with you, not against you.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Everything you are given is material for the next move. Everything.&#8221;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-2-quotes-from-others\">2 QUOTES FROM OTHERS<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>I.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Physician and educator <strong>Maria Montessori<\/strong> on leading others:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>&#8220;The greatest sign of success for a teacher is to be able to say, &#8220;The children are now working as if I did not exist.&#8221; But this holds true for leadership in general\u2014give people space and they flourish.&#8221;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Source: <\/em><a href=\"https:\/\/amzn.to\/42yjouU\">\u200b<em>The Montessori Method (1912)<\/em>\u200b<\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/amzn.to\/3UopMzXhttps:\/\/amzn.to\/42yjouU\">\u200b<em>\u200b<\/em>\u200b<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p>\u200bII.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Physicist and chemist <strong>Marie Curie<\/strong> on the connection between fear and knowledge:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>&#8220;Nothing in life is to be feared, it is only to be understood. Now is the time to understand more, so that we may fear less.&#8221;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Source: <\/em><a href=\"https:\/\/amzn.to\/4jElCil\">\u200b<em>Madame Curie: A Biography by Eve Curie<\/em><\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-1-question-for-you\">1 QUESTION FOR YOU<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A question from <a href=\"https:\/\/x.com\/nickcammarata\/status\/1876749765951562209\">\u200bNick Cammarata\u200b<\/a> to inspire action:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>&#8220;If I had 10x the agency I have, what would I do?&#8221;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Until next week,<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>James Clear <a href=\"https:\/\/jamesclear.com\/atomic-habits\">\u200b\u200b\u200b<\/a> <br><em>Author of <\/em><a href=\"https:\/\/jamesclear.com\/atomic-habits\">\u200b<em>Atomic Habits<\/em>\u200b<\/a><em> <\/em><br><em>Creator of the <\/em><a href=\"https:\/\/jamesclear.com\/3-2-1\">\u200b<em>3-2-1 Newsletter<\/em>\u200b<\/a><em> <\/em><br><em>Founding Author of <\/em><a href=\"https:\/\/authorsequity.com\/\">\u200b<em>Authors Equity<\/em>\u200b<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>p.s. <a href=\"https:\/\/x.com\/gonzotrucker\/status\/1004732672017510400\">\u200b<\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/jamesclear.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/Screenshot-2025-01-30-at-10.20.57\u202fAM.png\">You need a lift\u200b<\/a>?<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>3 IDEAS FROM ME I. &#8220;Beware the student of one teacher. A good idea spirals into dogma when it gets applied to everything and stretched beyond the areas where it is useful. Remain open and embrace a lot of teachers.&#8221; (\u200b\u200bShare this on X\u200b\u200b) \u200bII. &#8220;Your best performances will come when you are working in [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":40295,"menu_order":0,"template":"","acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO Premium plugin v20.5 (Yoast SEO v20.6) - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>3-2-1: On the danger of a good idea, how to do your best work, and a question to inspire action - James Clear<\/title>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/jamesclear.com\/3-2-1\/january-30-2025\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_US\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"3-2-1: On the danger of a good idea, how to do your best work, and a question to inspire action\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"3 IDEAS FROM ME I. &#8220;Beware the student of one teacher. A good idea spirals into dogma when it gets applied to everything and stretched beyond the areas where it is useful. Remain open and embrace a lot of teachers.&#8221; (\u200b\u200bShare this on X\u200b\u200b) \u200bII. &#8220;You